snippet.title: Your Favorite Free Golf Game | WGT Golf
snippet.description:
Join the millions of players who are competing now on more than 15 championship golf courses, free on WGT Golf!

Play famous courses, upgrade to virtual equipment from your favorite golf brands and compete against people all over the world in head-to-head games, tournaments and more.

Download free on iOS, Android and Amazon, or play online at wgt.com.

WGT Golf Mobile Game by Topgolf
